{"tid":1598802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動】民陣 928 添馬公園集會　獲批不反對通知書","createTime":"2019-09-27T16:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T10:16:47.000Z","uid":279356,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cc21740828a81ccf451658a0f582a720a3272b19","tid":1598802,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y1jsOt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy1jsOt9.jpg&h=36b1fa4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3-928-%E6%B7%BB%E9%A6%AC%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E7%8D%B2%E6%89%B9%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E6%9B%B8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2599%25A3-928-%25E6%25B7%25BB%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2589%25B9%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%259B%25B8%2F&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=29fb6311\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2599%25A3-928-%25E6%25B7%25BB%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2589%25B9%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%259B%25B8%2F&h=7716cad1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3-928-%E6%B7%BB%E9%A6%AC%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E7%8D%B2%E6%89%B9%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E6%9B%B8/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/928-08_QK7Pu_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F928-08_QK7Pu_1200x0.png&h=c72f2f03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民間人權陣線發起，9 月 28 日星期六晚上 7 時，在金鐘添馬公園集會，警方批出不反對通知書，時間由下午 3 時到晚上 10 時。至於民陣申請 10 月 1 日由銅鑼灣遊行到金鐘，不反對通知書申請未有結果。<br />\n<br />\n2014 年 9 月 28 日，警方在金鐘夏慤道發射 87 發催淚彈，觸發為期 79 日的佔領運動，民陣發起在 928 五週年，舉行「反抗威權 迎接黎明」集會，集會時間由晚上 7 時至 9 時。"},{"pid":"a2fc9eefb7be9d8fa8f45b6a3a56d617819718dd","tid":1598802,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EEN6jC8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEEN6jC8.jpg&h=5e7909fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EizXrh8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEizXrh8.jpg&h=56ed96d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U2MbvKP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU2MbvKP.jpg&h=c5f14b68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1eeb64bd2e5eb004885a2c81e4288a267a4da3b9","tid":1598802,"uid":241742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:11:22.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bbfdb1f36c2352e40ef9b4726beadfbf3354ff6","tid":1598802,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2fc9eefb7be9d8fa8f45b6a3a56d617819718dd","tid":1598802,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EEN6jC8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEEN6jC8.jpg&h=5e7909fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EizXrh8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEizXrh8.jpg&h=56ed96d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U2MbvKP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU2MbvKP.jpg&h=c5f14b68&s={SIZE}